Our garments don't shrink or fade . We use natural dyes completly free of harmful substances ( Oeko -Tex Standard 100 - Certification) . Each garment is made under a process of manual tinted with environmental friendly water-based dyes . Our printing system is a unique process that prints directly to the fibers of the products to ensure realism in the colors and durability. Thanks to this, our garments can be ironed without loosing their properties.


Characteristics :

  • 100 % premium cotton
  • Pre - washed, always keep their properties
  • Realistic Colors and Drawings
  • Water-based Dyes
  • Free of harmful substances (Certificación Oeko-Tex Standard 100)
  • Respectful of environmental sustainability
